---
layout: base.njk
pageKey: about
title: About
permalink: about.html
description: Symbio AI is two builders turning plain-English ideas into websites, booking systems, and AI agents that move revenue. If you can explain it, we can build it.
---

{# ===== Page head ====================================================== #}
<section class="section section--tight">
  <div class="container container--narrow center">
    <span class="eyebrow eyebrow--center">About Symbio AI</span>
    <h1 class="section__title">If you can explain it, we can build it.</h1>
    <p class="section__lead">
      Symbio AI is two builders who turn plain-English ideas into websites, booking systems,
      and AI agents that actually move revenue — without the agency runaround.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

{# ===== Vision ========================================================= #}
<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="grid grid--2 grid--top">
      <div data-reveal>
        <span class="eyebrow">Our vision</span>
        <h2 class="section__title">Most businesses don’t have a tech problem. They have a leak problem.</h2>
        <p class="text-lead mt-6">
          Leads show up — then slip away. No one replied fast enough, the site was confusing,
          or there was no easy way to book. We build the systems that catch those leads and
          convert them, and we keep it honest: a free scan before anyone talks money, real
          numbers, and software we’d happily use ourselves.
        </p>
      </div>

      <ul class="card__list" data-reveal data-reveal-delay="1">
        <li>Plain English in, working software out.</li>
        <li>A free scan before anyone talks money.</li>
        <li>Honest pricing and realistic timelines.</li>
        <li>We build only what actually moves revenue.</li>
        <li>You always have a direct line to the builders.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{# ===== Founders ====================================================== #}
<section class="section section--tint">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section__head" data-reveal>
      <span class="eyebrow">The team</span>
      <h2 class="section__title">Two people. Reachable directly.</h2>
      <p class="section__lead">No account managers, no hand-offs. You work with the people building it.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid--2">
      {% for person in site.founders %}
        <article class="founder" data-reveal data-reveal-delay="{{ loop.index0 }}">
          <span class="founder__avatar" aria-hidden="true">{{ person.name | first }}</span>
          <h3 class="founder__name">{{ person.name }}</h3>
          <p class="founder__role">{{ person.role }}</p>
          <div class="founder__contact">
            <a href="mailto:{{ person.email }}">✉ {{ person.email }}</a>
            {% if person.phone %}
              <a href="tel:{{ person.phone | replace(r/[^0-9+]/g, '') }}">☎ {{ person.phone }}</a>
            {% endif %}
          </div>
        </article>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{# ===== Process ======================================================= #}
<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section__head section__head--center" data-reveal>
      <span class="eyebrow eyebrow--center">The process</span>
      <h2 class="section__title">Scan → Map → Build → Polish</h2>
      <p class="section__lead">A simple, honest path from “it’s losing leads” to “it’s closing them.”</p>
    </div>

    <ol class="grid grid--4">
      <li class="step" data-reveal>
        <span class="step__num">1</span>
        <h3 class="step__title">Scan</h3>
        <p class="step__text">
          We review your site and funnel — for free — and tell you exactly where leads leak.
        </p>
      </li>
      <li class="step" data-reveal data-reveal-delay="1">
        <span class="step__num">2</span>
        <h3 class="step__title">Map</h3>
        <p class="step__text">
          We map the smallest set of changes that move revenue the most, and price it
          honestly.
        </p>
      </li>
      <li class="step" data-reveal data-reveal-delay="2">
        <span class="step__num">3</span>
        <h3 class="step__title">Build</h3>
        <p class="step__text">
          We build the site, booking, and AI agents — fast, to spec, and in plain sight.
        </p>
      </li>
      <li class="step" data-reveal data-reveal-delay="3">
        <span class="step__num">4</span>
        <h3 class="step__title">Polish</h3>
        <p class="step__text">
          We tune copy, speed, and follow-ups until the numbers actually move.
        </p>
      </li>
    </ol>
  </div>
</section>

{# ===== Closing CTA =================================================== #}
<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="cta-band" data-reveal>
      <h2 class="cta-band__title">Tell us what you want to build</h2>
      <p class="cta-band__text">
        If you can explain it, we can build it. Start with a free scan, or email us directly.
      </p>
      <div class="btn-row btn-row--center">
        <a class="btn btn--light btn--lg" href="{{ site.cta.url }}">Get my free scan</a>
        <a class="btn btn--secondary btn--lg" href="mailto:{{ site.founders[0].email }}">Email the team</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
